  "summary": "Malicious code in chain-chai-await (npm)",
  "details": "When required, chain-chai-await spawns a detached background process that fetches JavaScript code from hxxps://jsonkeeper[.]com/b/EXSIF and executes it via the Function constructor with full Node.js require access. The remote host (jsonkeeper[.]com/b/EXSIF) serves the second-stage payload. The parent process is unaware of the background execution (detached:true, child.unref()).",
